# 🎨 AI-Based Image Transformation Tool for Cartoon Effect

This project is an AI-powered tool that transforms real images into **cartoon-style artworks** using deep learning models (e.g., PyTorch or Stable Diffusion).

## 🚀 Features
- Converts normal photos into cartoon-style images.
- Multiple style variations (light, comic, oil, watercolor).
- User-friendly interface for uploading and downloading images.

## 🧠 Technologies Used
- Python
- PyTorch
- OpenCV
- NumPy
- Matplotlib

## ⚙️ Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/AI-Image-Transformation-Tool.git
cd AI-Image-Transformation-Tool
pip install -r requirements.txt

